curity,\nOAuth2/JWT\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nSenior Software Developer / Solution Architect\nWhitecap Canada — Canada\n2010 – Present\nArchitect and deliver secure, scalable software solutions for enterprise clients including\nMiele Canada, Woodbine Entertainment Group, Park'N Fly, Caplans, RiskCheck, HPIbet,\nOntario Sires Stakes, Thoroughbred Improvement Program, Travel Insurance Office."], 'metadata': [{'page_label': '2', 'author': 'Amir Nasser', 'created_by': 'd32936fd-7f4c-457e-8b0d-ffdd89e239b7', 'name': 'f_resume.pdf', 'file_id': '028cf161-63b9-4432-8e10-538dbb60ab0b', 'total_pages': 3, 'embedding_config': "{'engine': '', 'model': 'sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2'}", 'source': 'f_resume.pdf', 'page': 1, 'start_index': 898, 'hash': 'ffcca1525cd9390c7bd6f6c5df66fa6adf78e41c14900f00d2666627d7c1246c', 'producer': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC', 'moddate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'creationdate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'creator': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC'}, {'name': 'f_resume.pdf', 'author': 'Amir Nasser', 'page': 2, 'creationdate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'created_by': 'd32936fd-7f4c-457e-8b0d-ffdd89e239b7', 'file_id': '028cf161-63b9-4432-8e10-538dbb60ab0b', 'page_label': '3', 'creator': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC', 'source': 'f_resume.pdf', 'producer': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC', 'start_index': 0, 'hash': 'ffcca1525cd9390c7bd6f6c5df66fa6adf78e41c14900f00d2666627d7c1246c', 'total_pages': 3, 'moddate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'embedding_config': "{'engine': '', 'model': 'sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2'}"}, {'creationdate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'file_id': '028cf161-63b9-4432-8e10-538dbb60ab0b', 'hash': 'ffcca1525cd9390c7bd6f6c5df66fa6adf78e41c14900f00d2666627d7c1246c', 'source': 'f_resume.pdf', 'start_index': 865, 'moddate': '2026-02-13T09:31:03-05:00', 'name': 'f_resume.pdf', 'producer': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC', 'creator': 'Microsoft® Word LTSC', 'page': 0, 'author': 'Amir Nasser', 'created_by': 'd32936fd-7f4c-457e-8b0d-ffdd89e239b7', 'page_